00:19:15.820 --> 00:19:19.780
in a bank even you could
successfully pull it off.

00:19:19.780 --> 00:19:26.580
So that business was falling
out as well as the pending death

00:19:26.580 --> 00:19:28.500
of the gin running businesses

00:19:28.500 --> 00:19:32.480
which these guys were also
using to make their living.

00:19:32.480 --> 00:19:34.510
So they're getting
squeezed on two ends

00:19:34.510 --> 00:19:38.230
